# Snapshots

To switch: `snap <tag>`

---

## v1-simple-search

**Simple Search**

Basic search UI with results display.

---

## v2-dataline

**DataLine Component**

Search results with tags and links via DataLine component.

---

## v3-wide-layout

**Wide Grid Layout**

Full-width responsive grid with fixed-height cards.

---

## v4-filter-sort

**Filter & Sort Interface**

Category-based filter UI with tag selection, ribbon showing active filters with modifiers (none/+/!), and sorting by relevance/alphabetical/type. Press 'f' to toggle filters, Escape to close. Option+click filter icon to clear all.

---

## v5-cleanup

**Links, CORS & Cleanup**

Added links, CORS support, and general code cleanup.
